            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "John 5:14",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " to have arisen from some sin of his, from a vicious course of living, perhaps intemperance; so that he might be a middle aged man, when this distemper first seized him, and therefore must be now stricken in years: ",
            "children": []
