        "class": "",
        "text": "Wilt thou (θέλεις)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Not merely, do you wish, but are you in earnest? See on Matthew 1:19. Jesus appeals to the energy of his will. Not improbably he had fallen into apathy through his long sickness. Compare Acts 3:4; John 7:17.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "Not merely, do you wish, but are you in earnest? See on ",
